<h2><a https://yarnetsky.github.io/ontheriversedge/index.html?id=963" title="Our library&#8217;s photocopier is blushing"> Our library&#8217;s photocopier is blushing</a></h2>

<div class="entry">


     

  	<p>Another entry from out &#8220;only at a library&#8221; collection&#8230;.</p>

	<p>One of our assistants was picking up stray papers near our photocopier and found the original of a cut and paste worksheet on sign language.</p>

	<p>&#8220;Huh, sign language, that&#8217;s cool. What in the&#8230;?&#8221; and she laughed her head off.</p>

	<p>It was more than a dozen signs all dealing with sex. Use your imagination as to what signs were on the sheet.</p>

	<p>No, I won&#8217;t be publishing the results.</p>



 
<div class="line"></div>

