<h2><a https://yarnetsky.github.io/ontheriversedge/index.html?id=959" title="Only at a library&#8230;"> Only at a library&#8230;</a></h2>

<div class="entry">


     

  	<p>could this possibly happen.</p>

	<p>We got a video returned today where the box was chewed to pieces by a dog.</p>

	<p>Fortunately, the video was in one piece, but we were all rolling when we discovered the title. &#8220;Basic Dog Obedience.&#8221; It apparently failed to have an impact.</p>

	<p>Maybe the human should have been watching it instead of the dog.</p>



 
